        Nested Loop : Loop inside a loop is called a nested loop
        for(int i = 1; i<=5; i++){
            for(int j = 1; j<=5; j++){
                System.out.print("* ");
            }System.out.println();
        }


what will happen if we remove println after j loop
Ans - Everything will print horizontally

